    "body": "# Pull Request\n\n## Description\nThis PR introduces new, high-quality content focusing on \"AI Autonomous AI Systems 2026\" and \"AI Cognitive Computing Breakthrough 2026,\" along with a related case study. This new content is prominently advertised on the frontend through a new promotional banner, an enhanced content showcase, and updates to the content recommendation system and footer navigation. The goal is to enrich the site's content offerings and improve discoverability of cutting-edge AI topics for 2026.\n\n## Type of Change\n- [ ] New feature (non-breaking change which adds functionality)\n- [ ] Documentation update\n\n## Testing\n- [x] I have tested this change locally\n- [ ] I have added tests for this change\n- [x] All existing tests pass\n- [x] I have tested the build process\n\n## Checklist\n- [x] My code follows the project's style guidelines\n- [x] I have performed a self-review of my code\n- [ ] I have commented my code, particularly in hard-to-understand areas\n- [x] I have made corresponding changes to the documentation\n- [x] My changes generate no new warnings\n- [ ] I have added tests that prove my fix is effective or that my feature works\n- [x] New and existing unit tests pass locally with my changes\n- [x] Any dependent changes have been merged and published\n\n## Screenshots (if applicable)\nN/A\n\n## Additional Notes\nNew content includes:\n- Blog post: `app/blog/ai-autonomous-ai-systems-2026/page.tsx`\n- Blog post: `app/blog/ai-cognitive-computing-breakthrough-2026/page.tsx`\n- Case study: `app/case-studies/ai-cognitive-computing-success-2026/page.tsx`\n\nFrontend advertising updates:\n- Added `Revolutionary2026ContentBanner` to `app/page.tsx`.\n- Added `EnhancedContentShowcase2026` to `app/page.tsx`.\n- Updated `ContentRecommendationSystem` in `app/page.tsx` to feature new content.\n- Updated footer navigation in `app/layout.tsx` with links to new content.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-8ccfe0fb-9e51-4d98-b67d-af11e02d02ba\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-8ccfe0fb-9e51-4d98-b67d-af11e02d02ba\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-light.svg\"><img alt=\"Open in Web\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web.svg\"></picture></a>\n\n",
